light does not use borrowed money or leverage the firm does not generate large trading volumes in june  there were  employees including  analysts and  trader it occupies a single high floor of an office building near grand central in new york city historyedit a few months before the dotcom bust greenlight lost  of its total capital on a short on chemdex stock as it soared in price a few months after greenlight closed its position chemdex stock plunged to  in the third quarter of  greenlight lost  of its value primarily from long positions on industrial companies like helix energy solutions when the sec temporarily banned short selling of financial stocks with the majority of greenlights money in bonds and long positions on stocks this stopped hedge funds minimizing long losses or offsetting them with short gains greenlight ended  down  its first annual loss in  greenlight recouped its losses from  einhorn and greenlight capital were fined by the fsa for insider trading on the  january  greenlight capital was down  percent for  in february  greenlight capital was ranked rd out of  hedge funds with a d grade in the institutional investor’s alpha hedge fund report card this was the second year in a row greenlight capital received a d from iia top equity holdingsedit as of  the top equity holdings of the firm were in the shares of the following companies apple inc general motors marvell technology group cigna aetna computer sciences delphi automotive ncr corp virgin media and market vectors greenlight capital lowered its stake in apple by  percent to  million shares during the fourth quarter of  despite apple shares being up  percent in the year philanthropyedit political contributionsedit in  greenlight capital ranked th out of wnycs top  hedge fund political donors the hedge fund contributed  to new york state political campaigns in  greenlight capital made a total of  in political contributions in the  election cycle individuals within greenlight capital donated  to 